column2: SELECT   m.ra2 AS ra1, m.dec2 AS dec1, m.z, m.Search_radius/# AS Search_radius,    n.objid, n.distance,   o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.petroMag_i as imag into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.MyTable AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( m.ra2, m.dec2, m.Search_radius/#) AS n   JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   WHERE     o.type = #       order by m.ra2
